          "description": "The staff is very nice, caring and very considerate of children and parents. I wouldn\u2019t take my baby any where else. The emergency room is clean and the rooms are cozy. The nurses and doctors are so nice and attentive so is the staff.",
          "link": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m8!14m7!1m6!2m5!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pnNWRHb3RTamxpVFVWVGNFUXRTRmh3YldNeU9GRRAB!2m1!1s0x0:0x777ede51c64e1d8f!3m1!1s2@1:CAIQACodChtycF9oOjg5dGotSjliTUVTcEQtSFhwbWMyOFE%7C%7C?hl=en",
